1041
01:10:20,458 --> 01:10:22,833
[woman] Nobody's gonna care
what you're singing.

1042
01:10:22,916 --> 01:10:28,250
What they care about
is that you are a young, beautiful woman

1043
01:10:28,833 --> 01:10:30,541
with a voice of an angel.

1044
01:10:34,791 --> 01:10:36,375
[Beauty] What song should I do?

1045
