Okay.

1052
01:11:01,833 --> 01:11:05,666
Well, why don't you take this?

1053
01:11:05,750 --> 01:11:07,708
See if you can learn something.

1054
01:11:07,791 --> 01:11:12,208
Take these and see
what a couple of my big stars did

1055
01:11:12,291 --> 01:11:13,833
with their opportunity.

1056
01:11:14,875 --> 01:11:16,833
I have a conference call in five.

1057
01:11:26,208 --> 01:11:28,208
Kelly, get me Stevie on the phone.

1058
01:11:44,000 --> 01:11:45,083
[camera clicks]

1059
01:11:45,666 --> 01:11:48,583
[camera whirring]

1060
01:11:48,666 --> 01:11:50,250
[indistinct chattering]

1061
01:11:55,333 --> 01:11:57,208
Are you gonna go in?

1062
01:11:57,291 --> 01:11:58,375
[Jasmine] Hell, no.

1063
01:11:59,375 --> 01:12:01,958
[camera clicks, whirring]

1064
01:12:02,041 --> 01:12:03,833
[Beauty] Are you gonna come in with me?

1065
01:12:05,500 --> 01:12:06,916
[Jasmine] It's your brother.

1066
01:12:11,458 --> 01:12:12,916
[Beauty] What you doing here?

1067
01:12:14,125 --> 01:12:15,250
[Cain sighs]

1068
01:12:15,333 --> 01:12:16,333
[sniffles]

1069
01:12:17,083 --> 01:12:18,250
Daddy's sick.

1070
01:12:21,833 --> 01:12:22,916
What you mean?

1071
01:12:23,458 --> 01:12:24,791
He had a heart attack.

1072
01:12:26,875 --> 01:12:28,750
How come Mommy didn't call me?

1073
01:12:29,666 --> 01:12:30,708
She tried.

1074
01:12:31,875 --> 01:12:33,083
You ain't been home.

1075
01:12:38,333 --> 01:12:39,500
Where is he now?

1076
01:12:41,791 --> 01:12:44,875
He's at Saint Michael's
on the fifth floor.

1077
01:12:47,416 --> 01:12:48,958
He's been asking for you.

1078
01:13:04,833 --> 01:13:05,958
[elevator dings]

1079
01:13:15,541 --> 01:13:16,541
[Beauty] Daddy?

1080
01:13:17,958 --> 01:13:20,416
[Father breathing raggedly]

1081
01:13:25,125 --> 01:13:27,750
Hey, daughter.

1082
01:13:30,958 --> 01:13:32,083
How you feeling?

1083
01:13:32,666 --> 01:13:35,000
Hey, I've been better.

1084
01:13:37,625 --> 01:13:38,625
You know,

1085
01:13:39,875 --> 01:13:42,791
I'm sorry
I didn't come earlier to visit you. I...

1086
01:13:44,625 --> 01:13:46,291
I didn't know you were sick.

1087
01:13:48,750 --> 01:13:50,250
How's the album coming?

1088
01:13:51,833 --> 01:13:52,875
Really good.

1089
01:13:54,333 --> 01:13:55,333
[groans softly]

1090
01:13:59,333 --> 01:14:01,958
[Father breathes deeply]

1091
01:14:02,041 --> 01:14:04,208
They said they have to open me up,

1092
01:14:05,291 --> 01:14:06,625
work on my heart.

1093
01:14:08,583 --> 01:14:09,833
What's wrong with it?

1094
01:14:10,541 --> 01:14:12,875
Not getting enough blood or something.

1095
01:14:14,166 --> 01:14:17,166
- That's from eating all that pork.
- [chuckles]

1096
01:14:17,250 --> 01:14:18,791
I know you ain't talking.

1097
01:14:19,375 --> 01:14:20,833
You eat worse than me.

1098
01:14:20,916 --> 01:14:22,916
But I'm young. I can do all that.

1099
01:14:23,000 --> 01:14:24,166
[Father chuckles]

1100
01:14:25,666 --> 01:14:28,791
- If I don't make it outta here...
- Don't... don't say that.

1101
01:14:29,291 --> 01:14:31,458
Let me speak my piece, okay?

1102
01:14:37,083 --> 01:14:39,333
I've always been an ambitious man.

1103
01:14:40,750 --> 01:14:42,583
I got that from my father.

1104
01:14:44,166 --> 01:14:45,750
He had a hard life.

1105
01:14:46,750 --> 01:14:51,708
I think that's why I was so determined
to make something of myself.

1106
01:14:54,333 --> 01:14:56,791
I wanted my life to have meaning.

1107
01:14:59,916 --> 01:15:01,416
But after a while...

1108
01:15:02,625 --> 01:15:03,625
[chuckles softly]

1109
01:15:05,791 --> 01:15:09,166
...I realize I... have to settle

1110
01:15:09,250 --> 01:15:12,916
for just being the head of my house.

1111
01:15:14,833 --> 01:15:15,833
Shit.

1112
01:15:17,791 --> 01:15:19,625
I wasn't even good at that.

1113
01:15:21,750 --> 01:15:25,083
That's why it was so important

1114
01:15:26,333 --> 01:15:29,041
to me that you make it.

1115
01:15:32,458 --> 01:15:35,541
I thought, if you went far,

1116
01:15:36,375 --> 01:15:37,833
I would too.

1117
01:15:39,291 --> 01:15:40,291
I know.

1118
01:15:41,416 --> 01:15:44,333
[Father] That's why it's hard
for me to say this...

1119
01:15:47,250 --> 01:15:50,166
but I need you to give me my cut.

1120
01:15:54,583 --> 01:15:55,458
Cut of what?

1121
01:15:55,541 --> 01:15:57,642
[Father] I'm the one negotiated
that contract for you.

1122
01:15:57,666 --> 01:15:59,208
You know what? I'm not doing this.

1123
01:15:59,291 --> 01:16:02,291
[Father] I know you got
a new apartment downtown.

1124
01:16:02,375 --> 01:16:03,750
[Father inhales]

1125
01:16:03,833 --> 01:16:06,625
I even heard
you bought your little girlfriend a car.

1126
01:16:06,708 --> 01:16:08,333
Yeah, and where'd you hear that?

1127
01:16:10,500 --> 01:16:12,375
You can't keep nothing from me.

1128
01:16:17,750 --> 01:16:19,958
Is that why you wanted to see me?

1129
01:16:20,666 --> 01:16:26,333
[Father] All I need is
for you to pay me what you owe.

1130
01:16:32,416 --> 01:16:34,208
I don't owe you shit.

1131
01:16:35,333 --> 01:16:39,291
You owe me your whole life.

1132
01:16:43,000 --> 01:16:44,500
I used to think that.

1133
01:16:45,875 --> 01:16:47,250
But I don't anymore.

1134
01:16:49,541 --> 01:16:50,791
[Father] Look at you.

1135
01:16:50,875 --> 01:16:52,291
Just look at ya.

1136
01:16:52,875 --> 01:16:55,916
[chuckles] I didn't think
the business was gonna change you,

1137
01:16:56,000 --> 01:17:00,083
but you up in here acting all crazy,
and you ain't even had a hit record yet.

1138
01:17:07,250 --> 01:17:08,666
But one day, I will.

1139
01:17:10,708 --> 01:17:12,708
I'mma have a whole bunch of 'em.

1140
01:17:14,791 --> 01:17:18,000
And while I'm celebrating,
drinking champagne,

1141
01:17:19,583 --> 01:17:21,291
everybody will be there...

1142
01:17:23,458 --> 01:17:24,833
except for you.

1143
01:17:32,500 --> 01:17:35,083
Those the last words
you wanna say to your father?

1144
01:17:36,333 --> 01:17:39,125
Is that how you want me to remember you?

1145
01:17:45,750 --> 01:17:46,750
[sighs softly]

1146
01:17:52,791 --> 01:17:54,791
[somber music playing]

1147
01:17:57,958 --> 01:17:59,958
[indistinct chatter over speaker]

1148
